English subtitles for Binbou Shimai Monogatari (Poor Sisters' Story)

These are edited from their source translation, which was a mix of Melody and Doremi's original translations (with a bias towards Melody).

You are allowed to use these subtitles (and their accompanying typesetting) free of permission, charge, and any other restriction you can imagine, for any purpose you desire. Credit would be nice, but is by no means required.